E.JK", "IBOS.JK", "TIRA.JK", "PSDN.JK", "MAPB.JK", "ASJT.JK", "BIPP.JK", "CTBN.JK", "VOKS.JK", "SONA.JK", "VKTR.JK", "BSML.JK", "RELF.JK", "LMPI.JK", "KBAG.JK", "DEPO.JK", "IPPE.JK"], "timestamp": "2024-09-24T14:44:42", "title": "Bank DBS Indonesia Launches Investment Account Service with Competitive Interest Rate and US-Dollar-Based RDN Option"}, {"body": "PT Habco Trans Maritima Tbk (HATM) has formed a joint venture with Seacon Ships Management Group Limited, creating Horizon Sea Ships Pte, Ltd, with a 50% shareholding each and a fully paid capital of US$100,000. HATM reported a revenue of IDR 367.12 billion in the first semester of 2024, up from IDR 254.34 billion in the same period in 2023, with a gross profit of IDR 112.54 billion and a net profit of IDR 84.52 billion.", "dimension": {"dividend": 0, "financials": 2, "future": 0, "management": 0, "ownership": 0, "sustainability": 0, "technical": 0, "valuation": 0}, "sector": "transportation-logistic", "source": "https://www.idnfinancials.com/news/50980/hatm-teams-seacon-form-jv", "sub_sector": ["logistics-deliveries"], "tags": ["Earnings Report", "Mergers & Acquisitions", "Bullish"], "tickers": ["HATM.JK"], "timestamp": "2024-09-24T13:14:59", "title": "PT Habco Trans Maritima forms joint venture with Seacon Ships Management Group to enhance ship management services."}, {"body": "PT Solusi Kemasan Digital Tbk, a plastic packaging manufacturer, reported a net profit of IDR 1.29 billion in the first semester of 2024, representing an 11.2% year-on-year growth from IDR 1.16 billion in the same period last year. The company's sales also increased by 14.18% year-on-year to IDR 29.55 billion, driven by its plastic packaging products, with all sales coming from this segment.", "dimension": {"dividend": 0, "financials": 2, "future": 0, "management": 0, "ownership": 0, "sustainability": 0, "technical": 0, "valuation": 0}, "sector": "basic-materials", "source": "https://www.idnfinancials.com/news/50979/ipo-pack-profit-grows", "sub_sector": ["basic-materials"], "tags": ["Earnings Report", "IDX", "Financial Ratios", "Market Analysis", "Valuation", "Bullish"], "tickers": ["PACK.JK"], "timestamp": "2024-09-24T12:15:28", "title": "PT Solusi Kemasan Digital's net profit increases 11.2% to IDR1.29 billion in first semester 2024."}, {"body": "PT Remala Abadi Tbk acquired 85% of PT Fiber Media Indonesia's shares for IDR 19.97 billion, strengthening its position in the internet service provider sector and expected to increase market presence, service capabilities, and profit margins. In the first semester of 2024, Data reported revenue of IDR 127.47 billion, up 21% from the same period in 2023, with gross profit and profit also increasing by 52% and 60%, respectively.", "dimension": {"dividend": 0, "financials": 2, "future": 0, "management": 0, "ownership": 2, "sustainability": 0, "technical": 0, "valuation": 0}, "sector": "consumer-cyclicals", "source": "https://www.idnfinancials.com/news/50978/remala-abadi-takes-fiber-media-indonesia-shares", "sub_sector": ["retailing", "software-it-services", "technology-hardware-equipment"], "tags": ["Mergers & Acquisitions", "Earnings Report", "Bullish"], "tickers": ["DATA.JK", "ELIT.JK", "AXIO.JK", "YELO.JK"], "timestamp": "2024-09-24T11:05:47", "title": "Data acquires 85% of PT Fiber Media Indonesia shares for IDR 19.97 billion to strengthen its position in the internet service provider sector."}, {"body": "PT Green Power Battery has secured a contract worth IDR 139 billion to procure electric vehicle battery packs from PT Gotion Indonesia Materials, comprising 6,080 sets of electric motorcycle batteries worth IDR 21 billion and 31,080 sets of electric motorcycle battery packs worth IDR 118 billion. The battery packs will be handed over to PT Gotion Indonesia Materials after the agreement takes effect.", "dimension": {"dividend": 0, "financials": 2, "future": 0, "management": 0, "ownership": 0, "sustainability": 0, "technical": 0, "valuation": 0}, "sector": "energy", "source": "https://www.idnfinancials.com/news/50972/laba-secures-battery-pack-procurement-contract", "sub_sector": ["alternative-energy"], "tags": ["Energy Commodities", "IDX", "Bullish"], "tickers": [], "timestamp": "2024-09-23T17:00:04", "title": "PT Green Power Battery secures IDR 139 billion contract to supply electric vehicle battery packs to PT Gotion Indonesia Materials."}, {"body": "PT Jaya Konstruksi Manggala Pratama Tbk has injected IDR 7.51 billion in capital into PT Wika Tirta Jaya Jatiluhur, a company implementing a regional drinking water supply system project, with no material impact on operational activities. The capital injection was made on September 2, 2024, with PT Wijaya Karya Tbk holding an 80% stake in PT Wika Tirta Jaya Jatiluhur and the remaining 20% owned by PT Jaya Konstruksi Manggala Pratama and PT Tirta Gemah Ripah.", "dimension": {"dividend": 0, "financials": 2, "future": 0, "management": 0, "ownership": 2, "sustainability": 0, "technical": 0, "valuation": 0}, "sector": "infrastructures", "source": "https://www.idnfinancials.com/news/50971/jkon-channels-idr-capital-wika-tirta-jaya-jatiluhur", "sub_sector": ["heavy-constructions-civil-engineering"], "tags": ["Mergers & Acquisitions", "Bullish"], "tickers": ["JKON.JK", "WEGE.JK", "WIKA.JK"], "timestamp": "2024-09-23T16:18:52", "title": "PT Jaya Konstruksi Manggala Pratama Injects IDR 7.51 Billion into PT Wika Tirta Jaya Jatiluhur."}, {"body": "William Xiong, former VP of Alibaba Cloud Intelligence, has been appointed as Chief Technology Officer of PT GoTo Gojek Tokopedia Tbk, strengthening Alibaba Group's commitment to investing in the largest marketplace company. This strategic partnership aims to drive business growth and empower Indonesian businesses through digital innovation, combining Alibaba Cloud's cloud computing capabilities with GoTo's extensive ecosystem.", "dimension": {"dividend": 0, "financials": 0, "future": 0, "management": 2, "ownership": 1, "sustainability": 0, "technical": 1, "valuation": 0}, "sector": "technology", "source": "https://www.idnfinancials.com/news/50963/alibaba-official-appointed-cto-goto", "sub_sector": ["software-it-services"], "tags": ["Executive Changes", "IDX", "Fintech", "Bullish"], "tickers": ["GOTO.JK"], "timestamp": "2024-09-20T18:10:35", "title": "William Xiong appointed as Chief Technology Officer of PT GoTo Gojek Tokopedia to strengthen Alibaba's commitment to the company."}, {"body": "PT Barito Renewables Energy TBK's (BREN) share price plummeted 19.95% to IDR8,825 per share after being removed from the FTSE Russell index due to free float restrictions, aiming to prevent dominance by certain shareholders. The removal has led to BREN's stock price hitting its lowest point since August 15, 2024, making it subject to arbitrage trading on the Indonesia Stock Exchange.", "dimension": {"dividend": 0, "financials": 0, "future": 0, "management": 0, "ownership": 2, "sustainability": 0, "technical": 0, "valuation": 2}, "sector": "infrastructures", "source": "https://www.idnfinancials.com/news/50962/bren-share-price-plunges-kicked-ftse", "sub_sector": ["utilities"], "tags": ["IDX", "IDX Composite", "Market Trends", "Market Sentiment", "Stock Splits", "Bearish"], "tickers": ["BREN.JK"], "timestamp": "2024-09-20T15:48:57", "title": "Barito Renewables Energy's share price plummets 19.95% after removal from FTSE Russell index."}, {"body": "PT Barito Pacific TbK released 8 billion shares, causing its share portion to fall nearly half to 10.62%, while foreign investors participated in share reductions, including Prinsep Management Limited and Equatorex Sdn Bhd. Meanwhile, new share investments were made by BNYM ACP Fund I LP, acquiring 5.57% ownership of PT Apexindo Pratama Duta TbK, and I Nyoman Ehrich Lister, owning 7.17% of PT Royal Prima TbK's shares.", "dimension": {"dividend": 0, "financials": 0, "future": 0, "management": 0, "ownership": 2, "sustainability": 0, "technical": 0, "valuation": 0}, "sector": "basic-materials", "source": "https://www.idnfinancials.com/news/50961/barito-pacific-shares-chandra-asri-tpia", "sub_sector": ["basic-materials", "healthcare-equipment-providers", "oil-gas-coal"], "tags": ["Foreign Investor", "Executive Changes", "Mergers & Acquisitions", "Bearish"], "tickers": ["BRPT.JK", "APEX.JK", "PRIM.JK"], "timestamp": "2024-09-20T15:36:12", "title": "Barito Pacific sells 8 billion shares of Chandra Asri Pacific, multiple investors make significant transactions in various Indonesian companies."}, {"body": "The Indonesian government will hold an auction for state sharia securities (sukuk) next Tuesday, targeting IDR 8 trillion, with 7 series offered, including 2 SPN and 5 PBS series, with yields ranging from 4.87% to 6.87%. This is the 19th state sukuk auction this year, with a total of IDR 366.44 trillion in bids and IDR 159.87 trillion in won nominal value since the beginning of the year.", "dimension": {"dividend": 0, "financials": 2, "future": 0, "management": 0, "ownership": 0, "sustainability": 0, "technical": 0, "valuation": 0}, "sector": "financials", "source": "https://www.idnfinancials.com/news/50960/govt-holds-sukuk-auction-targets-idr-funds", "sub_sector": ["banks"], "tags": ["Sharia Economy", "Bonds", "Debt", "Bullish"], "tickers": [], "timestamp": "2024-09-20T13:10:31", "title": "Indonesian Government to Hold State Sukuk Auction Targeting IDR 8 Trillion with 7 Series on Offer"}, {"body": "PT Biomassa Lestari Nusantara's new wood pellet factory in Boyolali, Central Java, has a production capacity of 60,000 tons per year and is expected to support sustainable energy needs and boost the local economy. The factory, a joint venture between PT Dharma Energi Investama and Sumitomo Forestry Co. Ltd, aims to contribute to Indonesia's renewable energy development and optimize wood potential while promoting sustainable forestry practices.", "dimension": {"dividend": 0, "financials": 0, "future": 0, "management": 0, "ownership": 0, "sustainability": 2, "technical": 0, "valuation": 0}, "sector": "energy", "source": "https://www.idnfinancials.com/news/50959/dsng-ready-operate-boyolali-wood-pallet-factory", "sub_sector": ["alternative-energy"], "tags": ["Energy Commodities", "Timber", "Clean Energy", "Bullish"], "tickers": [], "timestamp": "2024-09-20T11:59:40", "title": "PT Biomassa Lestari Nusantara launches Indonesia's first wood pellet factory in Central Java, promoting circular economy and renewable energy."}]